Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.68,0:28:37.44,English,,0,0,0,,govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern\N{\rChinese}治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理 治理
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.44,0:28:43.40,English,,0,0,0,,govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern Okay,\N{\rChinese}治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.46,0:28:46.82,English,,0,0,0,,does that make sense? All right, and if you are an observer,\N{\rChinese}那样说通了吗？好了，如果你是观察者，
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.24,0:28:50.20,English,,0,0,0,,you think that what Iran did was right\N{\rChinese}你认为伊朗所做的是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.20,0:28:52.94,English,,0,0,0,,because it's a sense of fairness and justice, right?\N{\rChinese}因为这是一种公平正义的感觉，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.30,0:28:54.92,English,,0,0,0,,What Israel did was wrong.\N{\rChinese}以色列所做的是错的。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.06,0:28:58.44,English,,0,0,0,,It attacked an embassy of Iran in Damascus.\N{\rChinese}它攻击了驻大马士干的伊朗大使馆。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.54,0:29:01.58,English,,0,0,0,,That's against international law.\N{\rChinese}对国际法是违反的。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.54,0:29:06.14,English,,0,0,0,,And Iran, to save face,\N{\rChinese}伊朗为了保面子，
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.28,0:29:10.30,English,,0,0,0,,to pursue justice, threw some rockets at Israel.\N{\rChinese}为了追求正义，向以色列发射了一些火箭。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.30,0:29:13.46,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So most people think that\N{\rChinese}好的？所以大多数人认为是这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.46,0:29:16.62,English,,0,0,0,,Iran's response showed restraint and\N{\rChinese}伊朗的回应表现出克制，且是一次有度的回应。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.62,0:29:18.94,English,,0,0,0,,it was a measured response.\N{\rChinese}它是一种有节制的回应。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.18,0:29:23.04,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, does that make sense? All right, and the last thing is weaken the enemy.\N{\rChinese}好的，听得懂吗？好了，最后一点是让敌人变弱。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.28,0:29:24.76,English,,0,0,0,,Why would this weaken the enemy?\N{\rChinese}为什么这会让敌人变弱？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.98,0:29:26.58,English,,0,0,0,,Well, because\N{\rChinese}好吧，因为
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.58,0:29:30.20,English,,0,0,0,,after Iran attacked Israel,\N{\rChinese}在伊朗袭击以色列之后，
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.66,0:29:34.02,English,,0,0,0,,Israel wanted to show a strong response.\N{\rChinese}以色列想要展示强有力的回应。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.34,0:29:36.38,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? The reason why is that\N{\rChinese}好的？原因是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.38,0:29:40.28,English,,0,0,0,,Israel has a policy of disproportionality.\N{\rChinese}以色列实行不对称政策。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.46,0:29:49.40,English,,0,0,0,,So Israel is committed to disproportionality.\N{\rChinese}所以以色列已决定采取不对称行动。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.62,0:29:52.12,English,,0,0,0,,So what does that mean? It means that\N{\rChinese}那又意味着什么？就是这样：
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.12,0:29:55.04,English,,0,0,0,,if you kill one Israeli, they'll come\N{\rChinese}如果你杀了一个以色列人，他们就会来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.04,0:29:57.96,English,,0,0,0,,and kill about 100 of you, 1,000 of you.\N{\rChinese}并且杀掉你们大约一百人。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.06,0:30:01.74,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? If you throw one rocket at them, they'll throw 1,000 rockets at you.\N{\rChinese}好？如果你向他们发射一枚火箭，他们就会向你发射一千枚火箭。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.40,0:30:04.86,English,,0,0,0,,And the idea here is deterrence, right?\N{\rChinese}并且这里的想法是威慑，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.16,0:30:09.78,English,,0,0,0,,To make you afraid of Israel so you would not dare to think to attack Israel.\N{\rChinese}让你害怕以色列，才不敢想去攻击以色列。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.88,0:30:14.04,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So when\N{\rChinese}好的？那时
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.04,0:30:16.74,English,,0,0,0,,Iran attacked Israel,\N{\rChinese}伊朗攻击以色列
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.84,0:30:19.46,English,,0,0,0,,for the first time, by the way, this is the first time that\N{\rChinese}顺便说一句，这是伊朗第一次攻击以色列。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.46,0:30:22.14,English,,0,0,0,,Iran has attacked Israel, then\N{\rChinese}随后
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.14,0:30:25.66,English,,0,0,0,,Israel was committed to a disproportionate response.\N{\rChinese}以色列已决定作出不成比例的回应。
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.26,0:30:29.54,English,,0,0,0,,Who stopped Israel from a disproportionate response?\N{\rChinese}谁让以色列不再作出不成比例的回应？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.52,0:30:36.06,English,,0,0,0,,Who? Yes,\N{\rChinese}谁？是的，
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.26,0:30:39.96,English,,0,0,0,,why? Why would the United States say, Israel, do not attack?\N{\rChinese}为什么？美国会说‘以色列，别攻击’吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.08,0:30:45.68,English,,0,0,0,,govern Israel? govern Israel?\N{\rChinese}治理以色列？治理以色列？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.78,0:30:47.18,English,,0,0,0,,govern Israel? govern Israel? govern Israel?\N{\rChinese}治理以色列？治理以色列？治理以色列？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.24,0:30:52.20,English,,0,0,0,,govern Israel? govern Israel?\N{\rChinese}治理以色列？治理以色列？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.44,0:30:53.96,English,,0,0,0,,govern Israel? govern Israel? govern Israel?\N{\rChinese}治理以色列？治理以色列？治理以色列？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.28,0:30:55.62,English,,0,0,0,,govern Israel? govern Israel?\N{\rChinese}治理以色列？治理以色列？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.18,0:30:57.82,English,,0,0,0,,govern Israel? govern Israel? govern Israel? govern Israel? govern Israel? govern Israel?\N{\rChinese}治理以色列？治理以色列？治理以色列？治理以色列？治理以色列？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.20,0:31:01.18,English,,0,0,0,,govern Israel? govern Israel? govern Israel? govern Israel?\N{\rChinese}治理以色列？治理以色列？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.98,0:31:07.64,English,,0,0,0,,govern Israel? govern Israel?\N{\rChinese}治理以色列？治理以色列？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.64,0:31:09.88,English,,0,0,0,,So the United States had to restrain Israel,\N{\rChinese}美国必须限制以色列的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.41,0:31:13.50,English,,0,0,0,,and so this is creating conflict between Israel\N{\rChinese}于是这导致以色列之间的冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.50,0:31:15.40,English,,0,0,0,,and the United States, okay?\N{\rChinese}以及美国，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.79,0:31:20.02,English,,0,0,0,,So that's why, so in other words,\N{\rChinese}所以这就是原因，换句话说，
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.79,0:31:24.16,English,,0,0,0,,from a military dominance perspective,\N{\rChinese}从军事统治视角来看，
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.44,0:31:28.20,English,,0,0,0,,Operation True Promise accomplished nothing, okay, because you blew nothing up.\N{\rChinese}真承诺行动没有完成任何事，嗯，因为你没炸任何东西。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.48,0:31:32.28,English,,0,0,0,,But from an asymmetrical warfare perspective,\N{\rChinese}但从不对称战争的视角来看，
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.28,0:31:37.54,English,,0,0,0,,you accomplish all your four major goals,\N{\rChinese}你实现了四个主要目标
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.88,0:31:41.24,English,,0,0,0,,and that's why the Iranians claim success.\N{\rChinese}于是伊朗人就宣称成功。
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.14,0:31:44.54,English,,0,0,0,,And you can make the argument that from a strategy perspective,\N{\rChinese}你也可以说，从战略角度来看，
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.94,0:31:47.86,English,,0,0,0,,it was a very successful operation, okay?\N{\rChinese}这是一场非常成功的行动，嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.94,0:31:52.40,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? All right, any questions about this?\N{\rChinese}那有道理吗？好了，关于这点还有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.48,0:32:00.66,English,,0,0,0,,Anything you want to clarify,\N{\rChinese}你想补充什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.26,0:32:02.62,English,,0,0,0,,or you don't want to say? I don't really understand.\N{\rChinese}或者你不想说什么？我还没完全懂。
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.22,0:32:06.28,English,,0,0,0,,Does this make sense to you?\N{\rChinese}这有道理吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.90,0:32:20.28,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so Peter asked a great question, like,\N{\rChinese}好的，彼得问了个很好的问题，像是，
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.32,0:32:23.42,English,,0,0,0,,this war, how will it affect us?\N{\rChinese}这场战争，怎么会影响我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.48,0:32:26.90,English,,0,0,0,,We're going to the United States for college, we're Chinese students, okay,\N{\rChinese}我们要去美国读大学，咱们是中国学生，好的，
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.94,0:32:28.98,English,,0,0,0,,and the answer is this, okay, the answer is,\N{\rChinese}答案就是这样，好的，答案是，
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.00,0:32:38.64,English,,0,0,0,,in a world that's something called rules of engagement, govern govern\N{\rChinese}在一个被称为交战规则的世界里，治理治理
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.64,0:32:44.86,English,,0,0,0,,govern govern\N{\rChinese}治理治理
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.86,0:32:48.78,English,,0,0,0,,govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern\N{\rChinese}治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.80,0:32:55.04,English,,0,0,0,,govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern\N{\rChinese}治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理治理
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.04,0:33:00.44,English,,0,0,0,,govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern govern We allow\N{\rChinese}我们允许
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.44,0:33:05.80,English,,0,0,0,,that. We will not allow NATO to send\N{\rChinese}那样。我们不允许北约派遣部队与乌克兰人作战。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.80,0:33:08.80,English,,0,0,0,,troops to fight with the Ukrainians,\N{\rChinese}troops to fightwith the Ukrainians,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.84,0:33:13.52,English,,0,0,0,,but we will allow NATO and the United States to provide weapons and financing.\N{\rChinese}但我们会允许北约和美国提供武器和资金。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.72,0:33:17.80,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? This is what we call the rules of engagement, the rules of war.\N{\rChinese}这有道理吗？这就是我们所说的交战规则，战争规则。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.10,0:33:25.64,English,,0,0,0,,So the same thing would happen if the United States were to invade Iraq.\N{\rChinese}同样的事如果美国入侵伊拉克也会发生。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.64,0:33:27.12,English,,0,0,0,,Before the actual invasion,\N{\rChinese}在实际入侵之前，
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.66,0:33:30.50,English,,0,0,0,,there would be an agreement among all major parties, which\N{\rChinese}所有主要方会达成协议，
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.50,0:33:33.56,English,,0,0,0,,would include Iran, the United States, Russia,\N{\rChinese}其中包括伊朗、美国、俄罗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.80,0:33:35.90,English,,0,0,0,,China, Israel, about the rules of war.\N{\rChinese}中国、以色列，关于战事规则。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.26,0:33:37.22,English,,0,0,0,,And so\N{\rChinese}于是如此。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.22,0:33:42.64,English,,0,0,0,,one important rule of war is you're not allowed to use tactical nuclear weapons.\N{\rChinese}一条重要的战事规则是你们不可以使用战术核武器。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.00,0:33:46.18,English,,0,0,0,,Iran, you may have nuclear weapons, you're not allowed to use them.\N{\rChinese}伊朗，你们可能拥有核武器，但可使用。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.62,0:33:48.48,English,,0,0,0,,The United States, you have nuclear weapons.\N{\rChinese}美国，你们拥有核武器。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.66,0:33:52.44,English,,0,0,0,,Israel, you have nuclear weapons, but you are not allowed to use them in this war.\N{\rChinese}以色列，你们拥有核武器，但在此战中可使用。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.12,0:33:55.46,English,,0,0,0,,That would be the first agreement.\N{\rChinese}那将是第一个协议。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.46,0:33:58.60,English,,0,0,0,,The second agreement is that Russia\N{\rChinese}第二个协议是俄罗斯和中国可以在很有限的范围内提供援助。
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.60,0:34:03.60,English,,0,0,0,,and China are allowed to provide assistance in a very limited basis.\N{\rChinese}and China are allowed to provide assistance in a very limited basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.68,0:34:08.94,English,,0,0,0,,So China would probably provide weapons\N{\rChinese}所以中国可能会提供武器
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.94,0:34:10.62,English,,0,0,0,,and material, but\N{\rChinese}以及物资
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.62,0:34:13.70,English,,0,0,0,,this will not impact the relationship between China\N{\rChinese}这不会影响中美之间的关系。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.70,0:34:17.64,English,,0,0,0,,and the United States.\N{\rChinese}and the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.18,0:34:19.94,English,,0,0,0,,And during this war,\N{\rChinese}在这场战争期间，
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.14,0:34:24.30,English,,0,0,0,,China will maintain a position of what we call strategic military.\N{\rChinese}中国将保持我们所说的战略军事位置。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.72,0:34:27.12,English,,0,0,0,,Great. Great.\N{\rChinese}太好了。太好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.12,0:34:29.90,English,,0,0,0,,Great. Great.\N{\rChinese}太好了。太好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.90,0:34:31.76,English,,0,0,0,,Great. Great.\N{\rChinese}太好了。太好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.42,0:34:34.46,English,,0,0,0,,Great. Great.\N{\rChinese}太好了。太好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.56,0:34:40.50,English,,0,0,0,,Great. Great.\N{\rChinese}太好了。太好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.50,0:34:42.22,English,,0,0,0,,Great. Great.\N{\rChinese}太好了。太好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.60,0:34:44.16,English,,0,0,0,,Great. Great.\N{\rChinese}太好了。太好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.30,0:34:48.74,English,,0,0,0,,Great. Great.\N{\rChinese}太好了。太好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.74,0:34:50.92,English,,0,0,0,,If anyone attacks you, it will come to your aid, right?\N{\rChinese}如果有人攻击你，它会来援助你，对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.10,0:34:52.36,English,,0,0,0,,They will not sign this treaty\N{\rChinese}他们不会签署这份条约
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.78,0:34:55.62,English,,0,0,0,,because they need to maintain strategic ambiguity,\N{\rChinese}因为他们需要保持战略模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.08,0:34:59.64,English,,0,0,0,,okay? China and Russia do not want to be dragged into this war.\N{\rChinese}好的？中国和俄罗斯不想被牵涉进这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.88,0:35:03.64,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? Okay,\N{\rChinese}那有道理吗？好的，
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.74,0:35:06.24,English,,0,0,0,,so my guess is that\N{\rChinese}所以我的猜测是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.24,0:35:10.20,English,,0,0,0,,China will provide assistance to Iran, but on a very limited basis\N{\rChinese}中国会给伊朗提供援助，但仅限于非常有限的基础
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.76,0:35:13.00,English,,0,0,0,,and on a basis that the United States can accept.\N{\rChinese}并且以美国能接受的基础
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.00,0:35:16.36,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's the first thing.\N{\rChinese}好的，这是第一件事。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.36,0:35:18.52,English,,0,0,0,,Second thing is, listen,\N{\rChinese}第二件事是，听着，
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.74,0:35:23.30,English,,0,0,0,,I'm just making a prediction that this war will happen.\N{\rChinese}我只是做个预测，这场战争会发生。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.42,0:35:25.26,English,,0,0,0,,I don't know it's gonna happen, okay?\N{\rChinese}我不确定它会发生，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.86,0:35:28.36,English,,0,0,0,,You understand? I'm just your high school teacher.\N{\rChinese}你懂了吗？我只是你的高中老师。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.24,0:35:32.34,English,,0,0,0,,I'm not making the decisions, okay?\N{\rChinese}我不是在做决定，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.52,0:35:35.24,English,,0,0,0,,I'm just teaching you how to think about geopolitics.\N{\rChinese}我只是教你如何思考地缘政治。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.78,0:35:39.26,English,,0,0,0,,And third of all,\N{\rChinese}再来，第三点是，
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.96,0:35:43.12,English,,0,0,0,,when you're actually in the United States, you'll find that there's\N{\rChinese}当你真正来到美国时，你会发现有很多人对以色列很生气。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.12,0:35:45.04,English,,0,0,0,,so much anger at Israel\N{\rChinese}so much anger atIsrael
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.62,0:35:47.46,English,,0,0,0,,that no one's gonna listen to you. No one really cares about Chinese students.\N{\rChinese}那个人也不会听你的。没人真正关心中国学生。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.02,0:35:50.32,English,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?\N{\rChinese}你明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.14,0:35:52.44,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, at that point,\N{\rChinese}我的意思是，到那时，
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.56,0:35:57.36,English,,0,0,0,,most Americans will be extremely anti -war.\N{\rChinese}大多数美国人会极度反战。
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.44,0:36:01.42,English,,0,0,0,,It'll be like the Vietnam War where\N{\rChinese}就像越战那样
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.42,0:36:03.86,English,,0,0,0,,you have these massive,\N{\rChinese}你有这些大规模，
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.96,0:36:07.16,English,,0,0,0,,you have this massive protest and civil unrest\N{\rChinese}你们有这场大规模的抗议和民间动乱
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.16,0:36:09.38,English,,0,0,0,,because there were a lot of Americans who were against the war.\N{\rChinese}因为有很多美国人反对战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.78,0:36:11.84,English,,0,0,0,,And quite honestly, it was a pointless war.\N{\rChinese}说实话，那是一场毫无意义的战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.10,0:36:14.76,English,,0,0,0,,America accomplished nothing by fighting the war.\N{\rChinese}美国通过打这场战争没有取得任何成就。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.56,0:36:18.86,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so great question, Peter.\N{\rChinese}好的，太棒的问题，彼得。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.66,0:36:21.54,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense to you?\N{\rChinese}这对你来说有道理吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.32,0:36:23.60,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, any more questions?\N{\rChinese}好的，任何其他问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.62,0:36:31.52,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, great question, okay.\N{\rChinese}好的，太棒的问题，好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.62,0:36:34.96,English,,0,0,0,,So we talked about the idea of hubris, right?\N{\rChinese}于是我们谈到了自负的概念，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.04,0:36:39.38,English,,0,0,0,,Emperors have hubris. And\N{\rChinese}皇帝有自负。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.38,0:36:44.18,English,,0,0,0,,so Israel is a small nation, about eight, nine million people, right?\N{\rChinese}所以以色列是个小国，人口大约八九百万人，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.34,0:36:46.24,English,,0,0,0,,It's not the American empire. It's not the American empire.\N{\rChinese}它不是美帝国。它不是美帝国。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.00,0:36:48.38,English,,0,0,0,,The problem is this.\N{\rChinese}问题在于此。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.40,0:36:50.46,English,,0,0,0,,The problem is that if you look at the Middle East,\N{\rChinese}问题是如果你看中东，
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.62,0:36:54.74,English,,0,0,0,,the strongest military power in the Middle East is Israel by far,\N{\rChinese}中东最强的军力无疑是以色列
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.94,0:36:59.16,English,,0,0,0,,okay? Israel does not actually need American protection.\N{\rChinese}好吧？以色列其实不需要美国的保护。
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.44,0:37:02.80,English,,0,0,0,,If the entire Middle East got together and attacked Israel,\N{\rChinese}如果整个中东联手攻击以色列，
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.98,0:37:05.92,English,,0,0,0,,Israel would win because this happened twice before, right?\N{\rChinese}以色列会赢，因为之前已经发生过两次，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.10,0:37:08.48,English,,0,0,0,,In the Yom Kippur War and the Six -Day War.\N{\rChinese}在赎罪日战争和六日战争中。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.68,0:37:11.72,English,,0,0,0,,So militarily speaking, Israel is powerful.\N{\rChinese}从军事角度来看，以色列很强大。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.90,0:37:16.12,English,,0,0,0,,And quite honestly, if the United States were to retreat,\N{\rChinese}说实在，如果美国撤退，
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.12,0:37:20.26,English,,0,0,0,,from the Middle East, Israel would dominate, okay?\N{\rChinese}从中东来看，以色列会占据主导地位，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.56,0:37:23.26,English,,0,0,0,,So even though it does not look like an empire,\N{\rChinese}虽然它看起来不像帝国，
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.50,0:37:26.34,English,,0,0,0,,it's basically an empire, you understand?\N{\rChinese}它基本上就是一个帝国，你懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.18,0:37:31.70,English,,0,0,0,,So therefore, it suffers from hubris,\N{\rChinese}于是，它因自大而受苦，
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.92,0:37:36.06,English,,0,0,0,,okay? It's not gonna be strategic and flexible and creative.\N{\rChinese}好吧？它不会是战略、灵活、创意的。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.20,0:37:39.92,English,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to be because it has military dominance over everyone.\N{\rChinese}它不必因为拥有对所有人的军事实力而占据主导地位。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.24,0:37:43.32,English,,0,0,0,,But that's a very good question, okay?\N{\rChinese}但这确实是个很好的问题，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.48,0:37:46.10,English,,0,0,0,,Just because Israel is small, there's a reason why Israel is small.\N{\rChinese}仅仅因为以色列小，才有以色列小的原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.12,0:37:48.34,English,,0,0,0,,It does not mean it is weak. It's very, very powerful.\N{\rChinese}这并不代表它弱小，它非常非常强大。
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.80,0:37:54.36,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Any more questions?\N{\rChinese}好的？还有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.10,0:38:04.90,English,,0,0,0,,. Okay, the question is very interesting.\N{\rChinese}好的，问题很有趣。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.20,0:38:08.96,English,,0,0,0,,So is America constraining Israel?\N{\rChinese}那么美国在限制以色列吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.30,0:38:11.78,English,,0,0,0,,And you can make the argument both ways, okay?\N{\rChinese}你也可以双向论证，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.08,0:38:14.68,English,,0,0,0,,You can make the argument that, um,\N{\rChinese}你可以这样论证，嗯，
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.74,0:38:20.46,English,,0,0,0,,American presence in Israel is preventing\N{\rChinese}美国在以色列的存在正在发挥作用。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.46,0:38:24.56,English,,0,0,0,,Israel from starting a regional war, okay?\N{\rChinese}以色列从未发动地区战争开始，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.66,0:38:26.62,English,,0,0,0,,But you can also make the argument that\N{\rChinese}但你也可以这样论证，
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.62,0:38:29.60,English,,0,0,0,,Israel right now is using America to\N{\rChinese}以色列现在正利用美国来实现其地缘政治利益。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.60,0:38:33.64,English,,0,0,0,,pursue a lot of its geopolitical interest.\N{\rChinese}以色列现在正利用美国来实现其地缘政治利益。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.16,0:38:39.28,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so, um, so\N{\rChinese}好的，嗯，嗯，
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.28,0:38:41.30,English,,0,0,0,,it's a very complicated question, okay?\N{\rChinese}这是个非常复杂的问题，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.44,0:38:44.44,English,,0,0,0,,But I think that, um,\N{\rChinese}但我觉得，嗯，
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.66,0:38:48.60,English,,0,0,0,,I personally think that, um, I think that America, Israel are constraining Israel.\N{\rChinese}我个人觉得，嗯，我认为美国、以色列正在约束以色列。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.66,0:38:54.10,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Because\N{\rChinese}好的？因为
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.10,0:38:56.56,English,,0,0,0,,Israel needs American support.\N{\rChinese}以色列需要美国支持。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.31,0:39:00.20,English,,0,0,0,,And that constrains the actions of Israel.\N{\rChinese}并且这约束了以色列的行动。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.45,0:39:03.08,English,,0,0,0,,But if America were not around,\N{\rChinese}如果美国不在场内，
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.58,0:39:08.34,English,,0,0,0,,then it's possible that Israel unleashes the full amount of its military.\N{\rChinese}那么以色列有可能全力释放其军力。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.01,0:39:10.58,English,,0,0,0,,And its military is very, very powerful.\N{\rChinese}其军力非常、非常强大。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.38,0:39:15.02,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? All right?\N{\rChinese}好？全部好？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.12,0:39:20.00,English,,0,0,0,,But, um, if America were to lead the region,\N{\rChinese}但，呃，如果美国在该地区领先，
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.18,0:39:23.26,English,,0,0,0,,then I think Israel would become the dominant power in the region.\N{\rChinese}我认为以色列会成为该地区的主导力量。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.12,0:39:30.98,English,,0,0,0,,But, um, I think the same is true for, throughout the world.\N{\rChinese}但，呃，我认为同样的情况在全世界都成立。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.20,0:39:34.90,English,,0,0,0,,If America left Europe, who would become the dominant power?\N{\rChinese}如果美国离开欧洲，谁会成为主导力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.36,0:39:41.32,English,,0,0,0,,Germany, right? And if America left East Asia,\N{\rChinese}德国，对吗？如果美国离开东亚，谁，谁，谁会成为主导力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.46,0:39:42.96,English,,0,0,0,,who, who, who would become the dominant power?\N{\rChinese}who, who, who would become the dominant power?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.44,0:39:46.68,English,,0,0,0,,Japan, okay? Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}日本，对吗？这样说对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.02,0:39:50.78,English,,0,0,0,,So I would say that the regional powers right now are Germany,\N{\rChinese}所以我会说，当前的地区大国是德国，
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.20,0:39:53.60,English,,0,0,0,,Israel and Japan.\N{\rChinese}以色列和日本。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.88,0:39:57.08,English,,0,0,0,,And it's an American empire and it's an American empire and\N{\rChinese}又是美国帝国，又是美国帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.08,0:40:00.00,English,,0,0,0,,it's an American empire and it's an American empire and it's an American empire and it's an American empire and\N{\rChinese}它是美国帝国，它是美国帝国，它是美国帝国，它是美国帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.00,0:40:03.04,English,,0,0,0,,it's an American empire and it's an American empire and it's an American empire and it's an American empire and it's an American empire and it's an American empire\N{\rChinese}它是美国帝国，它是美国帝国，它是美国帝国，它是美国帝国，它是美国帝国，它是美国帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.04,0:40:06.06,English,,0,0,0,,and it's an American empire and it's an American empire and\N{\rChinese}又是美国帝国，又是美国帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.06,0:40:09.70,English,,0,0,0,,it's an American empire and it's an American empire and it's an American empire and it's an American empire\N{\rChinese}它是美国帝国，它是美国帝国，它是美国帝国，它是美国帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.70,0:40:12.92,English,,0,0,0,,and it's an American empire and it's an American empire and\N{\rChinese}又是美国帝国，又是美国帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.92,0:40:15.80,English,,0,0,0,,it's an American empire That's a great question, okay?\N{\rChinese}它是美国帝国。那是个好问题，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.10,0:40:18.80,English,,0,0,0,,So, first of all, listen,\N{\rChinese}先说一句，先听我说，
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.22,0:40:22.42,English,,0,0,0,,this is all theory and conjecture, right?\N{\rChinese}这全是理论和猜测，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.18,0:40:26.96,English,,0,0,0,,America has not expressed any intent of invading Iran,\N{\rChinese}美国尚未表明入侵伊朗的意图，
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.20,0:40:30.04,English,,0,0,0,,and if America does invade Iran,\N{\rChinese}如果美国真的入侵伊朗，
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.36,0:40:32.68,English,,0,0,0,,then chances are it will win the war, okay?\N{\rChinese}那么它赢得战争的机会就大了，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.34,0:40:37.06,English,,0,0,0,,But an invasion of Iran,\N{\rChinese}但若入侵伊朗，
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.54,0:40:41.94,English,,0,0,0,,if it loses the war,\N{\rChinese}如果它输掉这场战争，
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.14,0:40:44.60,English,,0,0,0,,it would basically mean the end of the American empire,\N{\rChinese}这基本意味着美国帝国的终结，
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.04,0:40:48.16,English,,0,0,0,,okay? And the reason why is, if you look at why empires collapse,\N{\rChinese}好的？原因是，如果你观察帝国崩溃的原因，
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.48,0:40:50.12,English,,0,0,0,,it's because of three reasons, okay?\N{\rChinese}这有三点原因，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.18,0:40:51.78,English,,0,0,0,,The first is the idea of extension,\N{\rChinese}第一点是扩张的概念，
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.16,0:40:53.36,English,,0,0,0,,okay?\N{\rChinese}好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.68,0:40:58.16,English,,0,0,0,,Over extension. It's doing too many things at once, okay?\N{\rChinese}过度扩张。它一次做太多事，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.24,0:41:01.28,English,,0,0,0,,It's fighting this war in Ukraine, it's fighting this war in Iran,\N{\rChinese}它在乌克兰打这场战争，在伊朗打这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.56,0:41:03.94,English,,0,0,0,,it's fighting this war everywhere, basically, okay?\N{\rChinese}它在各地打这场战争，基本上，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.14,0:41:05.94,English,,0,0,0,,The idea of over extension, that's the first reason.\N{\rChinese}过度扩张的概念，就是第一个原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.28,0:41:09.30,English,,0,0,0,,Second is the idea of debt.\N{\rChinese}第二点是债务的概念。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.76,0:41:13.32,English,,0,0,0,,It basically just runs out of money, right?\N{\rChinese}它基本上就是用完钱，没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.42,0:41:15.24,English,,0,0,0,,Because it's over extension. It's extended. And\N{\rChinese}因为它过度扩张。它已经扩张。然后
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.24,0:41:18.68,English,,0,0,0,,this leads to the idea of civil unrest,\N{\rChinese}这导致了内战的概念。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.04,0:41:20.50,English,,0,0,0,,okay?\N{\rChinese}好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.88,0:41:28.16,English,,0,0,0,,So the American empire is heading into a lot of trouble over the next 10 years,\N{\rChinese}美国帝国在未来十年将陷入多重困境。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.34,0:41:30.70,English,,0,0,0,,because all three things are happening at once, right?\N{\rChinese}因为三件事同时发生，没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.76,0:41:33.18,English,,0,0,0,,Over extension, debt, and civil unrest.\N{\rChinese}过度扩张、债务和内战。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.20,0:41:35.92,English,,0,0,0,,At the same time,\N{\rChinese}同时，
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.08,0:41:40.52,English,,0,0,0,,the American empire is extremely wealthy\N{\rChinese}美国帝国极其富裕
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.52,0:41:42.14,English,,0,0,0,,and extremely powerful.\N{\rChinese}极其强大
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.60,0:41:44.36,English,,0,0,0,,So even though...\N{\rChinese}即使……
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.36,0:41:47.00,English,,0,0,0,,Even though America loses the war,\N{\rChinese}即使美国在战争中失利，但仍无与之匹敌的同级国者。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.38,0:41:51.10,English,,0,0,0,,there's still no peer competitor to the United States.\N{\rChinese}但这意味着什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.54,0:41:53.36,English,,0,0,0,,But all that means is that\N{\rChinese}But all that means is that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.36,0:41:57.70,English,,0,0,0,,the world will divide into different regional blocks, okay?\N{\rChinese}世界将分成不同的地区集团，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.78,0:41:59.22,English,,0,0,0,,Where maybe Germany controls Europe,\N{\rChinese}或许德国掌控欧洲，
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.60,0:42:03.26,English,,0,0,0,,Japan controls East Asia, Israel controls the Middle East,\N{\rChinese}日本掌控东亚，犹太掌控中东
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.42,0:42:05.50,English,,0,0,0,,okay? So\N{\rChinese}好的？那么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.50,0:42:08.56,English,,0,0,0,,more of a parallel world, okay?\N{\rChinese}更像是平行世界，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.36,0:42:13.88,English,,0,0,0,,A multipolar world as opposed to a unipolar world where one nation controls everything.\N{\rChinese}多极世界与单极世界相对，单极世界由一国掌控万物。
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.06,0:42:19.64,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? The decline of the American empire is going to take decades,\N{\rChinese}好的？美国帝国的衰落将耗时数十年
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.88,0:42:22.98,English,,0,0,0,,possibly centuries, okay? But\N{\rChinese}可能是几个世纪，行吗？但
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.98,0:42:28.56,English,,0,0,0,,we'll talk about this in a future class.\N{\rChinese}我们将在未来的课上再讨论这个。
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.14,0:42:32.84,English,,0,0,0,,What will happen to America if it loses the war, okay?\N{\rChinese}如果美国在战争中失利会怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.90,0:42:34.84,English,,0,0,0,,Any more questions? Yeah?\N{\rChinese}还有别的问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.86,0:42:37.08,English,,0,0,0,,I'm not confused.\N{\rChinese}我没搞错。
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.26,0:42:40.86,English,,0,0,0,,So if you or America attack Taiwan,\N{\rChinese}所以如果你或美国攻击台湾，
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.96,0:42:43.38,English,,0,0,0,,they are going to up their interest in the country?\N{\rChinese}他们会进一步提升对该国的兴趣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.54,0:42:45.66,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. So that's a good question, okay?\N{\rChinese}好的。那是个不错的问题，嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.78,0:42:50.16,English,,0,0,0,,Like, okay, the ground invasion. What will provoke it?\N{\rChinese}像，好的，地面进攻。是什么会引发它？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.76,0:42:55.16,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And that's something that I want to spend a future class on.\N{\rChinese}好的？这正是我想在未来课程中展开的内容。
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.98,0:43:00.48,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? But listen, we've done a lot of wars, okay?\N{\rChinese}好的？不过听着，我们已经打过不少战争了，嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.58,0:43:03.80,English,,0,0,0,,We know that America doesn't really need a reason to fight a war.\N{\rChinese}我们知道美国不需要理由就能发动战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.46,0:43:06.40,English,,0,0,0,,Do you understand? It can just make up a reason.\N{\rChinese}你明白了吗？它可以随便编个理由。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.60,0:43:10.58,English,,0,0,0,,It doesn't care. So\N{\rChinese}它不在乎。所以
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.58,0:43:13.74,English,,0,0,0,,basically, the argument that I want to make is that...\N{\rChinese}基本上，我想说的论点是……
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.74,0:43:16.40,English,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not a war. It's like, if Trump wins the presidency,\N{\rChinese}嗯，这不是一场战争。就像，如果特朗普赢得总统职务，
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.74,0:43:20.54,English,,0,0,0,,then it's most likely that he'll start a war against Iran.\N{\rChinese}然后最有可能他会对伊朗发动战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.12,0:43:24.52,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? That's what I think. I think it will be Trump who initiates the war.\N{\rChinese}好？这就是我的想法。我认为是特朗普会发动战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.78,0:43:26.40,English,,0,0,0,,And I think that\N{\rChinese}我觉得……
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.40,0:43:29.68,English,,0,0,0,,it will happen maybe two years from now.\N{\rChinese}大约两年后会发生。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.02,0:43:33.56,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay. Okay.\N{\rChinese}好的。好的。好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.74,0:43:45.26,English,,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay. This is a very complicated question, okay?\N{\rChinese}好的。好的。这是一个非常复杂的问题，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.46,0:43:48.36,English,,0,0,0,,Like, what's the relationship between Israel and America?\N{\rChinese}像，伊朗和美国的关系是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.90,0:43:51.80,English,,0,0,0,,And the reason why it's complicated is\N{\rChinese}而它之所以复杂的原因是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.80,0:43:54.18,English,,0,0,0,,that there's something called the Israel lobby.\N{\rChinese}有个叫做以色列游说的东西。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.80,0:43:59.26,English,,0,0,0,,And again, we need to spend an entire class on the idea of the Israel lobby\N{\rChinese}再说一次，我们要花整节课来讲以色列游说的概念。
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.26,0:44:00.92,English,,0,0,0,,because it makes no sense.\N{\rChinese}因为这样才有意义。
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.58,0:44:04.62,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? It's really hard to understand by itself.\N{\rChinese}好吧？单独理解起来很难。
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.90,0:44:07.70,English,,0,0,0,,So I'll spend an entire class on the Israel lobby, and\N{\rChinese}于是我会把以色列游说当作整节课来讲。
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.70,0:44:11.94,English,,0,0,0,,then you'll understand why there's an alliance between Israel and America, okay?\N{\rChinese}然后你就会明白为什么以色列和美国会结盟，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.94,0:44:14.20,English,,0,0,0,,All right, but thank you, okay?\N{\rChinese}好的，感谢你，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.26,0:44:18.76,English,,0,0,0,,Any more questions? So just to summarize,\N{\rChinese}还有问题吗？所以先总结一下，
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.14,0:44:21.28,English,,0,0,0,,we will do a class on Jack's question,\N{\rChinese}我们将以贾克的问题为主题开课，
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.40,0:44:26.58,English,,0,0,0,,what will the war look like, and what will it mean for America if it loses the war.\N{\rChinese}战争会是什么样子？如果美国输掉战争又会怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.84,0:44:29.08,English,,0,0,0,,We'll also do a class on David's question, which is,\N{\rChinese}我们还会以大卫的问题为主题开课，
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.98,0:44:32.62,English,,0,0,0,,what's the relationship between Israel and America?\N{\rChinese}以色列和美国的关系是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.50,0:44:35.02,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Any more questions?\N{\rChinese}好吧？还有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.50,0:44:41.78,English,,0,0,0,,We will, yes. We'll also be talking about the rise of Japan and Germany.\N{\rChinese}我们会的，没错。我们还会讨论日本和德国的崛起。
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.78,0:44:43.46,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? All right.\N{\rChinese}好的？全部明白。
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.80,0:44:46.20,English,,0,0,0,,Any more questions? Okay, great.\N{\rChinese}还有问题吗？好的，太好了。
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.28,0:44:48.04,English,,0,0,0,,I'll see you next week, okay?\N{\rChinese}下周见，好的？
